    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《SOL幕府》中，你将扮演結月，一个曾经强大的武士家族的继承者，其家族被敌对氏族屠杀殆尽。如今，結月沦为浪人，在地球卫星——月球——光鲜亮丽的都市中展开复仇之路。在这个世界里，高耸入云的太空电梯、高速列车和奢华的街区鳞次栉比，幕府精英们享受着如同地球般的舒适生活，从人造重力到模拟昼夜交替，无奇不有。然而……在每一座璀璨城市的背后，无数的劳动者因为幕府的统治而生老病死，他们的辛勤劳作是幕府权力背后不为人知的引擎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/870e8601847b113d757b7862956e3e73.poster.avif?t=1765998919\" width=1170 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/870e8601847b113d757b7862956e3e73.webm?t=1765998919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/870e8601847b113d757b7862956e3e73.mp4?t=1765998919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索月球</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索你从未见过的月球。作为通往太阳系的行星门户，以及众多幕府家族的权力中心，这并非你所熟知的月球。生机勃勃、宏伟的城市，巍峨耸立的巨型设施，依山而建的采矿城市，以及象征幕府权力的纪念碑，共同构成了这颗天体的表面。这是一个既危险又美丽的地方，等待你去探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/d93387ad63cfb31258d36426f93fab11.poster.avif?t=1765998919\" width=1170 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/d93387ad63cfb31258d36426f93fab11.webm?t=1765998919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/d93387ad63cfb31258d36426f93fab11.mp4?t=1765998919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >太空武士战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >砍杀你的敌人。成为一名太空武士，意味着要精通你的武器、装备，甚至驾驭重力本身。多款武器类型任你选择，每一种都是经过重新设计和科技强化，专为跨星球战争而生的传统武器。运用你不断增长的战斗技能，从远处或近距离消灭敌人，在敌人的阵营中开辟一条血腥的毁灭之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/02736c9a67a2f9437cce2a034906d6e7.poster.avif?t=1765998919\" width=1170 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/02736c9a67a2f9437cce2a034906d6e7.webm?t=1765998919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/02736c9a67a2f9437cce2a034906d6e7.mp4?t=1765998919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超越血肉与钢铁</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身为终极太空武士，为你的武器注入不同的元素效果，在战斗中占据优势；收集基因拼接，定制专属技能，打造专属你的作战方式武器。从生物陶瓷皮肤到强化视力，不断升级进化，成为终极战神。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/b7b7e0f8841a748ac9bf95b27823318c.poster.avif?t=1765998919\" width=1170 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/b7b7e0f8841a748ac9bf95b27823318c.webm?t=1765998919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/b7b7e0f8841a748ac9bf95b27823318c.mp4?t=1765998919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >星空封建日本</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索月球上那些利用人造重力创造重力的繁华都市，每一座都致敬着日本历史上备受尊崇的时代，象征着太阳系幕府对太阳系的统治。透过重力辅助装备，穿梭于壮丽的太空封建生物群落，揭开一场早已被遗忘的秘密战争。但请做好准备，在这里，剑之道才是王道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/54219a2dec2b7a0e3235ef2e0395b3e2.poster.avif?t=1765998919\" width=1170 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/54219a2dec2b7a0e3235ef2e0395b3e2.webm?t=1765998919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/54219a2dec2b7a0e3235ef2e0395b3e2.mp4?t=1765998919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >反抗重力</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个全新的世界中，利用你的喷射背包和纳米纤维抓钩索进行穿梭和战斗。这些先进科技让你能够在不同的重力环境下无缝移动。征服严酷的月球地形，投身于血腥刺激的杂技战斗，摧毁你的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/1449153a669be3198ea7c42481d68265.poster.avif?t=1765998919\" width=1170 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/1449153a669be3198ea7c42481d68265.webm?t=1765998919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219360/extras/1449153a669be3198ea7c42481d68265.mp4?t=1765998919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >史诗级BOSS战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战动态十足、电影级的多阶段 Boss 战，考验你的辨识和利用敌人弱点的能力。随着战斗的激烈程度，配乐也会随之变化，包括由日本摇滚乐队 AliA 在内的众多才华横溢音乐人精心打造的动感曲目，为 SOL Shogunate 量身订造的精彩战斗曲，后续将公布更多音乐人與歌曲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
